00:09:43.239 --> 00:09:51.080
what do you want to personally achieve? So for me personally, what I talked earlier about is

00:09:51.080 --> 00:09:59.320
making the right decisions for patients based on data. It could be something completely different

00:09:59.320 --> 00:10:06.520
for you. It's most likely very different for you. But you need to know why you do these things so

00:10:06.520 --> 00:10:18.280
