00:12:15.400 --> 00:12:21.000
Make sure that it tells the story, that there's really something personal in it.

00:12:23.080 --> 00:12:28.919
Make sure that you know who you write that for. So that is a personal branding aspect.

00:12:28.919 --> 00:12:45.000
The second thing is regularly contribute on LinkedIn. It's so easy. Pick a topic that

00:12:45.000 --> 00:12:53.640
you're passionate about and then write about it at least once a week, at least once a week.

00:12:54.039 --> 00:13:00.599
And if you do that, you will increase your personal visibility. Now advanced,

00:13:01.960 --> 00:13:08.440
go to conferences. Libby just mentioned the Zippozzit conference. Attend that.

00:13:11.239 --> 00:13:20.520
Present there. Join communities where you present as well. That will help you a lot.

00:13:20.679 --> 00:13:27.159
I love it. These are all fantastic points. Definitely post on LinkedIn and it doesn't

00:13:27.159 --> 00:13:31.880
have to be a revelation. You can just share something that you learned recently, something

00:13:31.880 --> 00:13:39.559
that you're excited about. And I really encourage everybody to do that and keep going. You don't

00:13:39.559 --> 00:13:46.760
have to pretend you're an expert in anything. By the way, Libby, one thing. Just post about

00:13:46.760 --> 00:13:49.960
something that you wish you would have known two years earlier.

